-- Nokia Unveils Rebranded Mapping, Location Service Named ‘Here’
-- B y   P e t e r   B u r r o w s
-- 2012-11-13T17:43:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-13/nokia-unveils-rebranded-mapping-location-service-named-here-.html
Nokia Oyj (NOK1V) , the struggling Finnish
smartphone maker, unveiled a new mapping and location services
brand under the name Here and said it acquired a 3-D mapping
company.  Nokia’s new Here cloud computing-based map service will
deliver location data across operating systems, Chief Executive
Officer Stephen Elop said today at an event in  San Francisco . It
will create maps in real time based on current conditions, and
show each person’s favorite places and routes, Elop said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Peter Burrows in San Francisco at 
